  ["level_sitdown_marin.70"] = "So, you agree that making the members of the Liberation Front think about their ideological differences, it might help in stopping them?",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.71"] = "You tell me to fight words with words, but not which words.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.72"] = "Please, riddles will not help much in not plummeting this city into chaos. You tell me to fight words with words, but not which words.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.73"] = "What is the main incompatibility between the collectivist and the individualist wing?",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.74"] = "What did you say was the main incompatibility between the collectivist and the individualist wing? ",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.75"] = "What is the main incompatibility between the individualist and the realist wing?",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.76"] = "What is the main incompatibility between the realist and the collectivist wing?",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.77"] = "That in a collectivist society, the more charismatic will still be able to gain power by manipulating the collective.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.78"] = "That in a collectivist society, people will still be greedy and work for themselves, not the collective.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.79"] = "That in a collectivist society, people's individual needs are not respected. ",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.80"] = "Greetings, Doctor Olaru! I must say it is quite an honor to meet you. Your piece on the entering of eco-centric ideals into the mainstream is one of my favorite articles of the last decade.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.81"] = "Ms. Olaru, thank you for your time. Now, if you will excuse me, I have some terrorists to catch.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.82"] = "Yes, I think this is as good as a one-sentence definition can be.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.83"] = "Interesting definition, but I think the relationship between ideology and policy is reversed. Ideology is more of a construct of the subjective, manipulated by the ruling to justify a world order.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.84"] = "Interesting definition, but wrong, for it does not describe the particular differences between ideology and religion.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.85"] = "That in such a society, entities that accumulate massive wealth will gain the power to block competition through de-facto regulation. They will clog markets that otherwise work well.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.86"] = "That in such a society, people's animalistic aggression would be culturally amplified, which would allow them to implode upon themselves.  ",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.87"] = "That such a society could exist when human's destructive capacity was limited, but not in today's world in which nuclear bombs can wipe out entire cities. ",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.88"] = "That in such a society, the most wealthy will also own all the weaponry, allowing them to oppress everyone. ",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.89"] = "That such a society culturally pushes people to be as greedy as possible. This will limit humankind's ability to grow through cooperation. ",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.90"] = "What would you say is the main argument against individualist anarchism?",
