  ["level_sitdown_marin.94"] = "Were there any other terrorist groups in history that had a similar ideology?",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.95"] = "Which terrorist groups from history do you mention as having a similar ideology?",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.96"] = "What would you say is the main argument against this realist anarchism?",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.97"] = "Is there anything particular about the Liberation Front's belief in this ideology?",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.98"] = "Again, is there anything particular about the Liberation Front's belief in this ideology?",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.99"] = "Do you have any works you suggest I should read to further understand this ideology?",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.100"] = "What further works did you suggest? ",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.101"] = "It's simple. One depends on the existence of private property, the other one depends on it not existing.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.102"] = "It's simple. Greed is fostered by the culture of one and subdued by the culture of the other.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.103"] = "It's simple. Monetary policy in an individualist society must surely be based on a fractional reserve system to keep inter-bank interest rates low, which cannot happen in a collectivist society. ",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.104"] = "Well, collectivist anarchism doesn't oppose modern living based on mass-production - just its private ownership. The realist wing believes in the self-sufficient small communities, which cannot sustain mass-production.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.105"] = "Well, collectivist anarchism fosters a culture of solidarity so as to allow large-scale collaboration, as opposed to the realist wing believing in evolution through the conflict between communities.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.106"] = "Well, the collectivist wing has humanist ideological roots, while the other one holds to its ideological roots.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.107"] = "I think the individualist wing opposes any kind of social hierarchy, only supporting economic hierarchy. The realist wing believes in competing communities that can only survive with clear leadership.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.108"] = "I think the individualist wing believes in economic freedom rooted in an inalienable right to private property, while the realist wing believes that there is only that possession of what they can defend.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.109"] = "I think that the individualist wing's ideology is incompatible with the nationalistic fervor that the realist wing tries to foster. ",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.110"] = "I understand your department recently received a grant.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.111"] = "Is there anything particular about the Liberation Front's belief in individualism?",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.112"] = "What did you say is particular about the Liberation Front's belief in individualist anarchism?",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.113"] = "Were there any other terrorist groups in history that had a similar ideology?",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.114"] = "Which terrorist groups from history did you mention as having a similar ideology?",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.115"] = "Anton Drasko, an obvious member of the individualist wing, organized the bombing of a corporate building.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.116"] = "Helene Kufos, an obvious member of the collectivist wing, organized the bombing of a governmental building.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.117"] = "Lynda Bailey, an obvious member of the realist wing, organized the bombing of a commercial building.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.118"] = "I do not understand something about the attacks that they organized.",
