  ["level_sitdown_marin.260"] = "Each member has their own particular belief system I guess, so you could say that there are a lot of particularities. ",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.261"] = "",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.262"] = "As I said, there are many. Bakunin was the first to call for a violent revolution of the economically oppressed, instigated through terrorism which he called \"propaganda by the deed.\" Then you can read Marx or Kropotkin, and so many others.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.263"] = "",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.264"] = "Well, precious, yes. It is anarchistic in nature. But other than that, I am certain there is a plethora or different sub-ideological beliefs held by different members. ",
