  ["level_sitdown_marin.269"] = "",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.270"] = "Oh dear, you should take better notes. What would be more persuasive is to remind them that a world in which masses hold all the power is one that can more easily be enslaved by charismatic leaders.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.271"] = "",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.272"] = "Well sugar, the one you said sounded pretty decent. ",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.273"] = "They look jokingly towards the ceiling. ",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.274"] = "E toți niște mari nenorociți. ",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.275"] = "Se jura.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.276"] = "Well, love, as I said, I do have a lot of professional respect for them. They play a great Blitzkrieg that may ultimately cost them the war. ",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.277"] = "",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.278"] = "Yes, a very good argument. It is true that for anarcho-individualists who believe in very specific logical models, all hinging on the axiom that individuals act in their own best interest, such an argument would be hard to refute.",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.279"] = "",
  ["level_sitdown_marin.280"] = "Yes, a decent argument. Though, not too persuasive for an indoctrinated member. They'd just say that warfare is expensive when gun ownership is not legally hindered, and also when you can hire private police. A better argument might be to say that the wealthy could disrupt the free market by manipulating people into accepting economic regulations.",
