  ["level_sitdown_marin.296"] = "Well, one can argue that even fascism, in all its forms, from traditional Italian fascism to white nationalism, is just an expression of the same type of philosophy that stands at the core of this ideology. That the strong should freely be allowed to rule the weak. ",
